title: The Adventure Zone: Amnesty - Episode 26
description: The Pine Guard continue to chase down their target — but when said target can look or sound like anyone, how do they tell friend from foe? Duck goes on a field trip. Aubrey discovers a treasure trove. Ned makes a startling announcement.
author: shows@themcelroy.family (The McElroys)
